---
import Button from "../button.astro";
import PostsLoop from "../posts-loop.astro";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-7 lg:px-0">
  <h2
    class="text-4xl font-playfair font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#7699d4] pb-2"
  >
    My "Blog"
  </h2>
  <p class="mb-6 text-base text-text dark:text-text">
What is a blog exactly? Can this be considered a blog? I am not sure of the definition, but here you can at least see some of my writings.
  </p>

  <div class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto my-7 xl:px-0">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col items-start justify-start md:flex-row md:space-x-7"
    >
      <div class="w-full md:w-2/3 space-y-7">
        <PostsLoop count="3" />

        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-full py-5">
          <Button text="View All My Posts" link={`${base}/posts`} />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full mt-10 md:w-1/3 md:mt-0">
        <div class="pl-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold md:text-2xl text-xl font-playfair text-[#7699d4] tracking-tight pb-2">
            Currently Consuming
          </h3>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-4 text-sm text-text dark:text-text">
            <li class="">
              1.
              <span class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-text">Omavaraisuushaste.com</span>
              <br />
              <span class="text-text dark:text-text">(by Esa Juntunen)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="">
              2.
              <span class="ml-1 text-text dark:text-text">Greg James</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-text">All the best for the future</span>
            </li>
            <li class="">
              3.
              <span class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-text">Rahapodi</span>
              <span class="ml-1 text-text dark:text-text">(by Nordent)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="">
              4.
              <span class="ml-1 text-text dark:text-text">Checking</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-text">Huutokaupat.com</span>
              <span class="ml-1 text-text dark:text-text">too often</span>
            </li>
            <li class="">
              5.
              <span class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-text">Abba</span>
              <span class="ml-1 text-text dark:text-text">(still and always)</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
